<countdown>!
An example of the countdown time counter, which is often used on websites (for example, until the end of the action, etc., remains ...).
Simple but useful feature JS.

<soccer2>!
Moving an item by clicking the mouse.
A simple example from a textbook on JS.

<move_go>!
Moving an element is done with the arrow on the keyboard left-up-right-down.
Increase button 1, decrease button 3 (on the right side of the keyboard).
A simple example from a tutorial on js.
